reviews.text: Delicious Cantonese noodles with reasonable price.
A quick lunch
Very local hong kong style noodles.  Cheap and delicous!
Exciting wonton noodles.  Not much choice of other dishes.  Traditional Cantonese restaurant.  Old style.  No deco at all.  Must be skinny to seat in.  Popular with blue collar workers.
a very old style noodle shop that you can buy wuton noodles or beef noodles. the taste is nice too~!
